Isio Wanogho (amụrụ ya na Nọvemba 17, 1983) bụ onye Naijiria supermodel, columnist, painter, na Interior architect

O nwetala ihe nrite African Youth Society, nhọpụta Future Awards abụọ, ihe nrite FAB, ihe nrite Nigerian Model Achievers Award ma bụrụ onye nnọchi anya ndị ntorobịa site na Global Foundation for Peace, Unity, and Development

Ọ gbasooela ọtụtụ mbọ gụnyere: ịme ihe osise nke nwere kaadị ndị e ji aka mee n'afọ 2000, ịme ihe ngosi n'afọ 2002, onye na-egosi telivishọn n'afọ 2007, imewe ejiji n'afọ 2009 (mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, ọ malitere uwe 5000 dị ka otu n'ime ndị na-emepụta ihe atọ maka Lagos Carnival n'afọ 2010).
Isio a mụrụ na Naijiria biri ma gụọ akwụkwọ na Florence, Italy ebe ọ nwetara M.Sc na Interior Design
Mgbe ọ laghachiri Naịjirịa n'afọ 2012, o guzobere ụlọ ọrụ mmepụta ihe ya wee gaa n'ihu na ọrụ ya dị ka onye na-egosi onyonyo
Ọ maara asụsụ isii, mana ọ na-asụ naanị Bekee, Yoruba, Italian na ụmụ amaala “Broken English” nke ọma.
E zigara Wanogho na Mayflower School na Ikenne mgbe ọ dị afọ ise

Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ praịmarị na sekọndrị n'ebe ahụ ma bụrụ onye na-arụsi ọrụ ike na egwuregwu, edemede na ịgba egwu ya - Na-ekere òkè na arụmụka na asọmpi n'ime ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ na maka ụlọ akwụkwọ ahụ megide ụlọ akwụkwọ ndị ọzọ na Ogun Steeti
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ sekọndrị, Wanogho nọrọ afọ abụọ n'ụlọ na-amụ ihe iji nweta nnabata na kọleji
O ji oge ezumike ya na-ese ihe, na-ese ma na-ede uri tupu ọ nweta obi ike ịkọrọ ezinụlọ ya na ọ na-achọkarị ịchụso nrọ ya nke ịghọ onye ejiji.
Mana mgbe onye na-ahụ maka ihe nlereanya Otu Winpana chọtara ya ka ọ na-alọta site na ọmụmụ onwe ya, ọ gwara ndị ezinụlọ ya bụ ndị na-enweghị obi ụtọ na mbụ maka echiche ahụ mana ha mechara tụgharịa
Ka e mesịrị n'afọ ahụ, Wanogho zọrọ n'afọ 2002 QueenAfrik beauty pageant site na nkwado nke nne ya
Winpana na-elekọta ya mana Wanogho enwetaghị mmeri ma ọ bụ pụta dị ka onye ikpeazụ
Nnukwu ezumike Wanogho bịara mgbe a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye nlereanya maka onye na-emepụta DAVIDA n'afọ 2002 St
Moritz Style Selection - nnukwu ngosi ejiji na Naịjirịa n'oge ahụ
N'ime afọ ole na ole sochirinụ dị ka onye na-eme ihe ngosi, ọ bụ onye nlereanya maka ndị na-emepụta ihe na Naijiria ma bụrụ ihe ngosi maka Davida, Remi Lagos na HALLERO
N'afọ 2015, e kpughere Wanogho dị ka onye nnọchi anya mgbasa ozi maka DIESEL na Nigeria na ihu DIESEL@Centro na Nigeria.
Isio banyere n'ime ụwa mgbasa ozi na nkwukọrịta n'afọ 2006 mgbe e gosipụtara ya dị ka onye ọbịa na ihe ngosi The Nigerian International nke gosipụtara na Nigeria na UK

N'afọ 2007, ọ rụrụ ọrụ n'akụkụ Uche Agbai na IK Ikponwosa dị ka ihu mgbasa ozi maka Close Up in the Close Up Salsa Fresh Challenge ebe ọ gosipụtara dị ka onye na-egosi TV na onye na-ekwuchitere ya, na-akwado nzukọ mgbasa ozi na ndị nta akụkọ n'aha akara ahụ nye ndị nta akụkọ, yana ịgagharị ọtụtụ steeti nke mba ahụ, iji mee ka ndị Naijiria mara ebumnuche nke akara ahụ na ọrụ ahụ.
N'afọ 2009, Isio banyere oge niile n'ime TV na-egosi dị ka onye isi na-egosi maka Soundcity's affiliate Fashion Station: Spice TV ma rebranded, na-ewere De-laVega pseudonym
Dị ka onye isi ngalaba ya, Isio kwadoro ihe ngosi isii sitere na ndụ na ejiji, na mkparịta ụka gburugburu na ajụjụ ọnụ ndụ

Nke a mere ka ọ nweta ọtụtụ ndị na-akwado ya ma mee ka ọ banye n'ime egwu Globacom na ihe ngosi TV dị ka nwanyị na-egosi ya na IllRymz.
Afọ atọ ka e mesịrị, a mụrụ IDDS (Isio De-laVega Design Studios)

Merging functionality, aesthetics and style, the design firm services commercial and residential spaces In this she has been recognized and honored with multiple awards and nominations, among which are the 2010 FAB Award as Ihe ngosi kacha mma nke afọ 2010 Ihe nrite ihe nlere anya nke ndi ntorobịa nke ndị mba Afrika, NMAA kacha mma Model-Ngozi nke afọ 2010.
N'afọ 2014, ọ pụtara nke mbụ ya na ihuenyo ọla ọcha dị ka onye na-eme ihe nkiri na NdaniTv's Gidi Up dị ka Bibi
Ọnwa ole na ole ka e mesịrị, ọ pụtara dị ka nwanyị na-edu ndú na obere ihe nkiri Ikechukwu ‘Killz’ Onanaku; Badt Guy
Mgbe ọ lọtara na Florence, Italy, Wanogho guzobere ụlọ ọrụ mmepụta ihe (Isio De-laVega Design Studios) nke na-enye ọrụ mmepụta ihe maka ndị ahịa ụlọ na ndị ahịa.
Wanogho na-enye aka na ndị na-enweghị ihe ùgwù na ndị ọrịa site n'inye ego ọ na-enweta kwa ọnwa n'ụlọ ụmụ mgbei ma na-akwụ ụgwọ ahụike nke ndị ọrịa n'enweghị aha
Echiche ya banyere nhụjuanya, ọrịa na agụụ na-akpali site na nkuzi nne na nna ya nke ọmịiko na ekele, na ọtụtụ afọ ọ nọrọ na Mayflower School, ụlọ akwụkwọ obibi dị anya site n'ụlọ nwata ya
Ọ hụrụ n'onwe ya n'ebe ahụ mmetụta anụ ahụ, mmetụta uche na nke uche nke ileghara anya, ịkpa ókè, nhụjuanya na enweghị.
Ọ na-eduzi ndị na-eto eto nlereanya site na Celebrite Modelling School na mmemme ya kwa afọ The Model Workshop, ma nwee peeji nke ndụmọdụ na Mara Mentors online ikpo okwu.
N'afọ 2008, Wanogho nwetara B.A na eserese na ihe ọkpụkpụ na Mahadum nke Lagos
Iji mezue ọrụ ya, ọ bụ Onye egwu Naijiria-Edosa Ogiugo duziri ya
Dị ka onye na-ese ihe, ihe nketa agbụrụ Urhobo ya bụ nnukwu mmetụta na nka ya, ebe ọ bụ na mpaghara Niger-Delta nke Nigeria, site na mpaghara Urhobo.
Site na nwata, a na-adọta Wanogho mgbe niile na ngosipụta okike site na nka, ya bụ eserese, ịbụ abụ na ide egwuregwu na obere akụkọ
O gosipụtara nka ya na Florence, Italy, na Lagos na Port Harcourt na Total E&P (TEPNG) nke afọ 2013 ngosi nka
N'afọ 2014, o nyere aka na International Art Festival. Nka bụ onyinye Wanogho kwenyere na a ejịrị wee mụọ ya.

Na Jenụwarị, 2014 Isio malitere ibipụta ihe odide ya site na kọlụm kwa izu na magazin BellaNaija, nke a na-akpọ Isio Knows Better N'ime nke a, ọ na-ejikọta ọgụgụ isi, satire na ahụmịhe onwe onye iji dọta ndị na-ege ntị ka ha chee nsogbu siri ike, mmekọrịta mmadụ na ibe ya na esemokwu ndị a na-echekarị banyere ha mana ọ na-adịkarịghị ekwukarị banyere ha ma ọ bụ mee ihe na obodo Naijiria.
N'afọ 2015, kọlụm Isio Knows Better ghọrọ ihe a ma ama, nke mere na ndị na-akwado Wanogho rịọrọ ya site na mgbasa ozi ọha na eze ka ọ bidokwa ide ihe mgbe ọ kwụsịrị ide ihe ruo izu isii.
